      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The wreckage you see in the mirror is the result of a massive, painful loss, and it's completely understandable that you feel like there's nothing left to save. But the core of who you are—the person underneath the reputation—is still there, even if it feels buried under ash. Even when everything seems gone, there are still small pieces of yourself that deserve to be seen and cared for. Please consider reaching out to someone who can help you navigate this profound sense of loss.",
