    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"person underneath.\" that person was the success. that person was the impact. without the career and the status, it's just a shell. i'm just a name in a disgraced headline now. it feels like there's no point in trying to dig through the ash to find something that's already fundamentally broken. it just feels like a waste of energy to keep pretending there's a path back when the bridge is gone.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
